Bayelsa State – The lady pictured here reportedly took her life yesterday by drinking the deadly insecticide known as Sniper because she had issues with her boyfriend. According to reports, she sells fruits at Azikoro town, opposite former PDP Chairman’s road, Yenagoa, Bayelsa State. Her body has been deposited at the morgue as her family, and close friends mourn her untimely demise. The Nigerian government has banned the open sale of Sniper at the market place but some individuals still have access to it. Source